From: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Tue, 10 Feb 2026 21:50:34 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] ==== damon_reclaim: introduce monitoring intervals autotune
 ====

mm/damon/reclaim: support monitoring intervals auto-tuning

The monitoring intervals auto-tuning feature of DAMON has proven to be
useful in multiple environments.  Add a new DAMON_RECLAIM parameter for
supporting the feature, and update the document for the new parameter.

Changes from v1
- v1: https://lore.kernel.org/20260501011740.81988-1-sj@kernel.org
- None.
Changes from RFC
- rfc: https://lore.kernel.org/20260414052855.90123-1-sj@kernel.org
- Add notes about behavioral changes that introduced by the auto-tuning.

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
